the long silence ( italian : il &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; silenzio , german : zeit des &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; , french : le long silence ) is a 1993 &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; political thriller-drama film directed by margarethe von trotta . for her performance in this film carla &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; was awarded best actress at the 1993 montreal world film festival and won the italian golden globe for best actress . the film also won the italian golden globes for best original score and for best screenplay .